   <topic>OBJECT.QUICKFILTER Function</topic>
            <description><![CDATA[The <OBJECT>.QUICKFILTER() method returns a count of the matching records, as if you had clicked the Quick Filter  icon.
]]></description>
   <syntax>Record_Count as N = .Quickfilter()</syntax>
<arguments>
<argument>
<name>Record_Count</name>
<description>The number of records found by the query.</description>
</argument></arguments>
 
   <sections>
     <section>
       <figure><link>images/Quick_Filter_button.gif</link></figure>
     </section>
     <section>
       <description><![CDATA[
The <OBJECT>.QUICKFILTER() method applies to:]]></description>
     </section>
       <section>
           <list>
<item>
<name><![CDATA[Browses (for <OBJECT> use either the <BROWSE> pointer or the name of the browse)]]></name>
</item>

<item>
<name><![CDATA[Forms (for <OBJECT> use either the <FORM> pointer or the name of the form)]]></name>
</item>

           </list>
       </section>



   </sections>
   <limitations>Desktop applications only.</limitations>
